text: Imyan-Kuper () is a rural locality (a selo) in Chukadybashevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 123 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 57 km from Tuymazy, 3 km from Alexeyevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Imyan-Kuper
